HEADWORD: Linchpin
<hw>Linch"pin`</hw> <pr>(l⟦icr⟧nch"p⟦icr⟧n`)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos>
<ety>[AS. <ets>lynis</ets> the axletree; akin to D. <ets>luns</ets>
